      • withEqualities

        public final CollectionCmpSameBuilder<O> withEqualities(java.util.List<java.util.function.Function<O,?>> equalities)
        Compare matched items based on equalities. All equalities must match in order for items to be considered equal.

        Equality is a function that takes item as an input parameter and returns a value. Two items are considered equal if the results of all it's equalities are equal.

        You can use this option to compare items of same type based on a few of their fields.

        Parameters:
        equalities - equalities based on which objects are compared
        Returns:
        builder instance
